</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection box="[1442,2645,2226,2260]" pageId="198" pageNumber="802" type="activity">
<paragraph blockId="198.[1442,2648,1872,2378]" box="[1442,2645,2226,2260]" pageId="198" pageNumber="802">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1442,1676,2226,2260]" pageId="198" pageNumber="802">Activity patterns.</emphasis>
The Mount Oku Wood Mouse is presumably arboreal and nocturnal.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
